    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Backcountry trail races, emergency rescue missions, and epic off-road adventurers, little monster truck fanatics will be swooning over this awesome 3pc monster truck playset from Kidplokio! The off-road, rock crawler monster truck toys feature a cool and rugged outdoor monster truck toys theme, pull-back friction power, and come with x1 monster truck, x1 removable trailer, and x1 ATV. Available in blue, red, or green colorways. The monster truck toys with ATV come ready to rock right out of the box! Kids can begin playing immediately, with no batteries or complicated assembly required, and no small pieces or instructions to keep track of</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio Monster Trucks Toy ATV Off Road Friction Trailer Pull Back Cars</h2>\n  <p>Backcountry trail races, emergency rescue missions, and epic off-road adventurers, little monster truck fanatics will be swooning over this awesome 3pc monster truck playset from Kidplokio! The off-road, rock crawler monster truck toys feature a cool and rugged outdoor monster truck toys theme, pull-back friction power, and come with x1 monster truck, x1 removable trailer, and x1 ATV. Available in blue, red, or green colorways.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>3PC MONSTER TRUCK TOYS - This awesome 3pc monster trucks playset from Kidplokio features a cool outdoor monster truck theme, pull-back friction power and includes x1 monster truck, x1 removable trailer, and x1 ATV for all your little one’s epic off-road adventures!</li>\n    <li>FRICTION POWERED - These monster truck toys come ready to rock right out of the box; kids can begin playing immediately by pulling back on the truck creating tension, and then watching the toy zoom away with or without the trailer and ATV!</li>\n    <li>PRETEND PLAY - Not only will little aspiring monster truck drivers be occupied for hours, but they’ll also be engaging in crucial early educational activities like working on their gross and fine motor skills, as well as growing cognitive development through imaginative playtime sessions</li>\n    <li>NO BATTERIES OR ASSEMBLY - No complicated assembly or batteries are required to operate these monster truck toys, meaning playtime can begin right away and there are no small pieces to keep track of</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Box dimensions:</strong> 17” x 5.5” x 5”; Weight: .90lbs; Colors: Assorted; Material: Plastic; Warning: Choking Hazard, small parts, recommended ages 3+</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/toys/6603D-3_friction_vehicle_offroad_BLU_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"Backcountry trail races, emergency rescue missions, and epic off-road adventurers, little monster truck fanatics will be swooning over this awesome\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPMONATV</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058486172</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 3pc</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The monster truck toys with ATV come ready to rock right out of the box! Kids can begin playing immediately, with no batteries or complicated assembly required, and no small pieces or instructions to keep track of. By simply pulling back on the monster trucks to create tension, kids and toddlers can watch their cars zoom speedily across the room, with or without the trailer and ATV.</p>\n  <p>And, not only will little aspiring monster truck drivers be thrilled and occupied for hours, they’ll be engaging in crucial early educational activities like working on their gross and fine motor skills, as well as increasing cognitive development through imaginative pretend play.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
